  • Irwin Musical Luna: Anaheim Comic Con [I have never seen this before and picked her up at a good price! You press her back and she'll meow, move her head and tail, and the Sailor Moon Theme will play. Very cute! I googled her and I found a page that showed the Japanese version which I'd never seen before either. Anyone have that one? I'd love to hear it talk!]
